source:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_SEQ_00<tab>Uin Nee's favorite leafmen are in need of a good pruning.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
target:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_SEQ_00<tab><var 48 F201FC /var><var 49 F201FD /var>特殊ルール： レベルアジャスト受注クラス・ジョブ制限<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>
※本クエストは受注時のクラス・ジョブでのみ進行します。

リダ・ラーンのウィン＝ニイは、草人の様子が気になっているようだ。

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_TODO_00<tab>Examine the overgrown leafmen and obtain leaves.
target: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_TODO_00<tab>モサモサ草人を調べ、<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FED01 /var>を入手

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the leafmen's leaves to Uin Nee.

TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_001<tab>Oh, but which of them was my favorite? Is it the one who once tried to sneak up on me and pluck my wings? Or the one who was just <var 1A 02 /var>so<var 1A 01 /var> cute when he confessed his love to me that I simply <var 1A 02 /var>had<var 1A 01 /var> to keep him by my side forever and a day!
target:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_001<tab>ねぇ<var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>さん、お願いがあるの！
ワタシたちのカワイイ草人は知っているでしょう？

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_002<tab>You've seen my collection of delightful little leafmen, have you not? Always basking blithely in the light of the sun, sprouting new fronds here, there, and everywhere!
target:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_002<tab>いつもお日さまの光を浴びて、気持ちよさそうにしているけど、
おかげで体の枝葉もボウボウに伸び放題……
むさ苦しいったらありゃしないわ！

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_003<tab>I had a mind to give them a little trim from time to time, but pointy objects are too prickly and perilous for my liking, don't you know. But <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>, my favorite mortal─you don't seem the type to be bothered by blades and shears, now do you?
target:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_003<tab>刈って整えてあげたいけど、ワタシ、鉄の刃物を使うのは苦手なの。
あの子たちのところをまわって、
「モサモサ草人」を可愛く整えてきてくれないかしら？

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_004<tab>So why don't you run along and give my foliating friends a little trim? And don't forget to bring back some of their pretty little leaves! The children in the Garden of Dreams do so much love to pile them up and jump inside!
target:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_004<tab>刈り取った<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FED01 /var>は、
夢に持ち込むものの材料にするから、持ち帰ってきてね。
それじゃあ、よろしく頼むわっ♪

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_SYSTEM_000_010<tab>Abundant green foliage sprouts from every nook and cranny of the leafman's body, such that many of the leaves and branches have become matted and tangled together.
target:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_SYSTEM_000_010<tab>草人の体から、元気よく枝葉が飛び出している。
なんとも生命力を感じる有り様だ。

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_SYSTEM_000_011<tab>With a few snips, you remove the overgrowth from the leafman's body, leaving it looking as prim and trim as the day it was born!
target: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_SYSTEM_000_011<tab>余分な枝葉を刈り取って、草人らしい丸いフォルムを取り戻した！

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_020<tab>Was there something you needed? Oh, but of course! You were going to prune my precious little leafmen for me. Well, did you?
target:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_020<tab>ありがとう、草人を整えてきてくれたのね！
<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E8FED01 /var>も、持ってきてくれたかしら？

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_021<tab>Thank you ever so much! I knew there was a reason why you were my favorite mortal. Oooh, and look at these lovely fronds you've brought back for me! Why, perhaps I'll spin them into a little leafman for the children!
target:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_021<tab>うんうん、これだけあれば十分だわ！
この枝葉に魔法をかけて、夢の中に持ち込む人形にするのよ。
もとがヒトだからかしら、活き活きしてカワイイんだから！

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_022<tab>Some of them don't have so many friends, you know? It truly breaks my heart to see. And so I'll fashion them a whole horde of leafmen to play with! They should get along swimmingly─after all, the leafmen used to be mortals, too!
target:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_022<tab>ワタシたちが夢で遊ぶ子どもは、寂しがりやさんが多いの。
夢の中に、たくさんの友だちを用意してあげたら、
いっぱい遊べて、きっと喜んでくれるわ！

source: TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_023<tab>Sometimes I wonder what it's like to be a leafman. Have you ever wondered, too? If you have, why, that could certainly be arranged! You need only say the─wait, why are you backing away from me like that?
target:
TEXT_BANPIX104_03692_UINNEE_000_023<tab>ウフフっ♪
また草人の枝葉が伸びてきちゃったら、お願いさせてね！
